  <zone type="main">
    <line>again turning towards the lifeless form of his</line>
    <line>creator he seemed to forget my presence while</line>
    <line>every feature &amp; gesture seemed instigated</line>
    <line>by the wildest rage. That is also my victim,</line>
    <line>he exclaimed—In his murder my crimes are</line>
    <line><add><ptr target="c57-0182.01"/></add>consum<mod>
        <add place="superlinear"><del rend="smear"><unclear reason="illegible" precision="low"
              unit="chars" extent="1">m</unclear></del></add>
        <add place="sublinear">m</add>
      </mod>ate<del rend="strikethrough">d</del> – Oh Frankenstein – Generous &amp;</line>
    <line>self devoted creature dare I ask <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">you</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">thee</add>
      </mod> to</line>
    <line>pardon me – I who destroyed thee by des</line>
    <line>troying those <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">thou</del>
        <del rend="strikethrough">you</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">thou</add>
      </mod> loved<add place="intralinear" resp="#pbs">st</add>. Alas he is</line>
    <line>dead and may not answer me.</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:p"/>
    <line>His voice seemed suffocated &amp; my</line>
    <line>first impulse which had been <del rend="strikethrough">at first</del></line>
    <line>to obey the dying request of my friend in</line>
    <line>destroying his enemy <del rend="strikethrough">do</del> now <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">died</del>
        <del rend="strikethrough">away</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">was overwhelmed</add>
      </mod> in</line>
    <line>a mixture of curiosity &amp; pity. I approach</line>
    <line>ed him – yet I dared not look on him</line>
    <line>there was somthing so
