    <line>in his ugliness. I attempted to speak but</line>
    <line>the words died away on my lips – The Monster</line>
    <line>continued to utter wild &amp; incoherent</line>
    <line>self reproaches at length I said. Your</line>
    <line>repentance is now useless. If you had felt</line>
    <line>the stings of remorse before you urged</line>
    <line><del rend="strikethrough">to extremity</del> your diabolical vengeance <add
